query:
SELECT se.*, s.name as subjectName, lm.id as moduleId, lm.title as moduleTitle
FROM subjectEnrollments se
LEFT JOIN subjects s ON se.subjectId = s.id
LEFT JOIN learning_modules lm ON lm.subjectId = se.subjectId AND lm.userId = se.userId
WHERE se.subjectId = 120001 OR s.name LIKE '%Inform%'
LIMIT 20;
